[
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Architecture & Modèle de Données"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "heading_2",
    "heading_2": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "1. Structure de la Base de Données (PostgreSQL)"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "La base de données PostgreSQL de Kased-App utilise un modèle relationnel hautement performant où la logique métier est déportée au niveau de la base de données via des contraintes de clés étrangères, des déclencheurs (triggers) et des procédures stockées (fonctions SQL)."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "heading_3",
    "heading_3": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Table "
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "membres"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "code": true
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Stocke les informations personnelles et administratives des membres de l'église."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "code",
    "code": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "CREATE TABLE membres (\n    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),\n    nom VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,\n    prenom VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,\n    date_adhesion DATE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_DATE,\n    date_naissance DATE,\n    telephone VARCHAR(20),\n    notes TEXT,\n    is_active BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT TRUE,\n    created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n    updated_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\n);"
          }
        }
      ],
      "language": "sql"
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "heading_3",
    "heading_3": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Table "
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "cultes"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "code": true
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Représente chaque réunion dominicale ou événement pour lequel des cotisations sont perçues."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "code",
    "code": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "CREATE TABLE cultes (\n    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),\n    date_culte DATE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_DATE,\n    titre VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL,\n    montant_cotisation NUMERIC(15, 2) NOT NULL CHECK (montant_cotisation >= 0),\n    notes TEXT,\n    created_by UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id),\n    created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n    updated_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\n);"
          }
        }
      ],
      "language": "sql"
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "heading_3",
    "heading_3": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Table "
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "cotisations"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "code": true
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Table de jointure liant un membre à un culte avec son statut de paiement."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "code",
    "code": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "CREATE TABLE cotisations (\n    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),\n    membre_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES membres(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,\n    culte_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES cultes(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,\n    statut statut_cotisation NOT NULL DEFAULT 'non_paye',\n    montant NUMERIC(15, 2) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0 CHECK (montant >= 0),\n    date_paiement TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE,\n    notes TEXT,\n    created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n    updated_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n    CONSTRAINT unique_membre_culte UNIQUE (membre_id, culte_id)\n);"
          }
        }
      ],
      "language": "sql"
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "heading_2",
    "heading_2": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "2. Le Type Énuméré "
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "statut_cotisation"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "code": true
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Pour garantir l'intégrité absolue des données de cotisation, nous utilisons un type énuméré PostgreSQL strict. Cela empêche l'insertion de statuts invalides ou erronés :"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "bulleted_list_item": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "`non_paye`"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " : Le culte a eu lieu et le membre n'a pas encore payé sa cotisation."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "bulleted_list_item": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "`paye`"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " : Le membre a réglé sa cotisation (le dimanche même ou lors d'un rattrapage)."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "bulleted_list_item": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "`absent`"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " : Le membre était absent ce dimanche-là. Aucune cotisation n'est due."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "bulleted_list_item": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "`en_avance`"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " : Le membre a payé sa cotisation en avance, avant même la tenue du culte."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "code",
    "code": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "CREATE TYPE statut_cotisation AS ENUM ('non_paye', 'paye', 'absent', 'en_avance');"
          }
        }
      ],
      "language": "sql"
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "heading_2",
    "heading_2": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "3. Vues SQL Calculées en Temps Réel"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Afin d'éviter des calculs lourds et lents côté client (Flutter) et d'assurer une source de vérité unique, la logique de synthèse est gérée par des Vues SQL indexées."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "heading_3",
    "heading_3": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "v_dashboard"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "code": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " (Statistiques Globales)"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Affiche les métriques clés de l'application sur l'écran d'accueil."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "code",
    "code": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "CREATE VIEW v_dashboard AS\nSELECT \n    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM membres WHERE is_active = TRUE) AS total_membres_actifs,\n    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM cultes) AS total_cultes,\n    (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT membre_id) FROM cotisations WHERE statut = 'non_paye') AS membres_en_retard,\n    (SELECT COALESCE(SUM(montant), 0) FROM cotisations WHERE statut = 'paye' OR statut = 'en_avance') AS total_collecte_fcfa;"
          }
        }
      ],
      "language": "sql"
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "heading_3",
    "heading_3": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "v_retards_membres"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "code": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " (Suivi des Retards)"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Identifie instantanément les membres ayant des impayés et calcule leur dette accumulée."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "code",
    "code": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "CREATE VIEW v_retards_membres AS\nSELECT \n    m.id AS membre_id,\n    m.nom,\n    m.prenom,\n    COUNT(c.id) AS nombre_retards,\n    SUM(cu.montant_cotisation) AS total_du_fcfa\nFROM membres m\nJOIN cotisations c ON m.id = c.membre_id\nJOIN cultes cu ON c.culte_id = cu.id\nWHERE c.statut = 'non_paye' AND m.is_active = TRUE\nGROUP BY m.id, m.nom, m.prenom;"
          }
        }
      ],
      "language": "sql"
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "heading_2",
    "heading_2": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "4. Architecture de l'Application Flutter"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "L'application respecte les principes de l'architecture propre (Clean Architecture) orientée données réactives avec "
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Riverpod"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " :"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "code",
    "code": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │                         UI COUCHE                           │\n │     [Widgets] ──► [Screens (Dashboard, Cultes, Membres)]     │\n └──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘\n                                │ Watch / Read State\n                                ▼\n ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n │                    STATE MANAGEMENT (Riverpod)              │\n │     [AppDataProvider]  ◄──►  [StatsProvider]                 │\n └──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘\n                                │ Fetch / Sync\n                                ▼\n ┌──────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────┐\n │                      SERVICES & NETWORKING                  │\n │   [Isar Local Database]   ◄──►   [InsForge Service (Dio)]   │\n │   (Caching Hors-ligne)           (Appels API PostgREST)     │\n └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘"
          }
        }
      ],
      "language": "plain text"
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "bulleted_list_item": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Local Database (Isar)"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " : Base de données locale NoSQL ultra-rapide fonctionnant comme cache. Elle stocke les données pour permettre à l'application de démarrer et de fonctionner instantanément, même sans connexion Internet."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "object": "block",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "bulleted_list_item": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Dio & InsForge Service"
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " : Dio gère la communication HTTP REST vers le BaaS InsForge avec des politiques de relance automatique et un timeout global robuste."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
]